# dexterMST 0.9.6

* fix for bug on mac introduced in 0.9.6

# dexterMST 0.9.5

* minor change to accomodate a new version of dexter


# dexterMST 0.9.3

* Fixed a bug that caused problems with MST designs with early exit - as in an MST designed to select the best candidates and testing 
  stops after a few modules.  

# dexterMST 0.9.2

* Changes required by Ripley to use Cairo 

# dexterMST 0.9.1

* fix for a bug in profile_tables for last routing with >2 modules
* Website package has changed

# dexterMST 0.9.0

* addition of Baysesian estimation method for CML

* fix for a bug in calibration of polytomous items

* new function `sim_mst` to simulate data for an mst design


# dexterMST 0.1.2

* minor changes to prepare for dexter version 1.0

* column name sumScore, outputted by profile_tables_mst changed to booklet_score

# dexterMST 0.1.1

* This release mostly to prepare release of new dexter version and maintain compatability


# dexterMST 0.1.0

* You may want to take a look at the companion packages, dexter and dextergui

